Subject: Connection problems between Linux agent and administration console
Description:
The Linux agent was manually installed on the computer, previously configuring the file with the server IP, port and group name data.

The installation is successful, but this computer is not reflected in the console.

The computer's firewall has been disabled but the communication problem persists
What_We_Know__c: Some lines from the option.sh script were not un-commented(3 export lines). After that it worked.
Solution_Comment__c: Some lines from the option.sh script were not un-commented(3 export lines). After that it worked.
